      <strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong><br />
       Contribute to the application of engineering and scientific principles to meet technical requirements.<br />
       Assist in the development of technical concepts, planning for implementation, and monitoring of technical progress. Support designs, tests, and assesses performance data. Contribute to the development of solutions to technical problems.<br />
       Assist senior engineers<br />
       Assist in the production of technical reports and other technical products, such as overall project concepts and descriptions, test plans, and technical reports.</p>
